001package org.biopax.paxtools.impl.level3;
002
003import org.biopax.paxtools.impl.BioPAXElementImpl;
004import org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.Level3Element;
005import org.biopax.paxtools.util.*;
006import java.util.Set;
007
008
009/**
010 * Base BioPAX Level3 element.
011 *
012 */
013public abstract class L3ElementImpl extends BioPAXElementImpl
014        implements Level3Element
015{
016    private Set<String> comment;
017    
018    public L3ElementImpl()
019    {
020        this.comment = BPCollections.I.createSet();
021    }
022
023    public Set<String> getComment()
024    {
025        return this.comment;
026    }
027
028    public void setComment(Set<String> comment)
029    {
030        this.comment = comment;
031    }
032
033    public void addComment(String COMMENT)
034    {
035        if(COMMENT != null && COMMENT.length() > 0)
036                this.comment.add(COMMENT);
037    }
038
039    public void removeComment(String COMMENT)
040    {
041        if(COMMENT != null)
042                this.comment.remove(COMMENT);
043    }
044}
